===[[Pokémon Masters EX]]===
{{main|Victor (Masters)}}
Victor forms a [[sync pair]] with {{p|Rillaboom}}, {{p|Spectrier}}, and {{p|Greedent}} in [[Pokémon Masters EX]]. His Rillaboom is capable of [[Gigantamax]]ing, while his Spectrier is capable of [[Dynamax]]ing. Victor became a playable sync pair on October 7, 2022.

Victor first appeared as an NPC during the [[solo event]] [[Severely Strained Relations]]. Victor has also made notable appearances in one of the game's main stories, the [[villain arc]]. Unlike in the original game, both Victor and {{mas|Gloria}} coexist in this game.

